LIKE A PRO","feature_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/5c43247014c11ad7a7f80df23fffbbd21a1627e6.jpg","feature1_title":"Personalized To Fit You","feature1_text":"Most bedding is made for the masses. Performance® bedding is built for you.\u2028Personalized to fit your body type, sleep position, and temperature preference, BEDGEAR delivers the optimal comfort, support, and alignment needed for game-changing sleep that fuels every tomorrow.","feature2_title":"Engineered For Cool Sleep & Recovery","feature2_text":"Cool sleep isn’t just more comfortable—it’s essential for recovery.\u2028That’s why every layer of a Performance® sleep system is powered by patented cooling technologies that deflect heat, wick moisture, and maximize airflow—so your body can fully rest, recharge, and recover overnight.","feature3_title":"Trusted By Pro Athletes","feature3_text":"The sleep gear of choice for professional athletes who rely on quality sleep to stay at the top of their game. <a href=\"\/\" style=\"color: #00b5e3\">Learn more<\/a>","button_text":"Shop All","button_link":"shopify:\/\/collections\/shop"}},"main":{"type":"main-page","disabled":true,"settings":{"padding_top":28,"padding_bottom":28}},"hero_alternating_blocks_VgeU7z":{"type":"hero-alternating-blocks","blocks":{"feature_block_jRVJKh":{"type":"feature_block","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/4bb311519d30258b3ec151b64288d3f68275e3cc.png","label":"NIGHT ICE PERFORMANCE® PILLOW","title":"3X Cooling Power","description":"<p>In the game of keeping you cool, Night Ice is a triple threat player.\u2028Instant-cooling Ver-Tex™ cover. Check. React™ Cooling Crown. Check. ICE Active Core. Check. And to box out any lingering heat, our patented Air-X® mesh and air vents keep fresh air flowing all night long. Three cooling layers. One unstoppable defense against heat.<\/p>","button1_text":"Shop Night Ice","button1_link":"shopify:\/\/products\/night-ice-performance-pillow","button2_text":"Take the Quiz","button2_link":"shopify:\/\/pages\/pillowid-quiz","image_on_left":true}},"feature_block_Ezik3T":{"type":"feature_block","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/7677a657feead63f3f153a88b5335a3c4ded1ef2.png","label":"M3 PERFORMANCE® MATTRESS","title":"Built Different. Built For You.","description":"<p>The first of its kind. Developed for elite recovery, the M3 features an innovative modular design that lets you choose your firmness on both sides of the bed—so you and your partner each get the comfort and support you need. Its instant-cooling cover and breathable layers disperse heat and enhance airflow to keep you cool all night long. This is comfort without compromise, personalized for how you sleep.<\/p>","button1_text":"Shop M3 Mattress","button1_link":"shopify:\/\/products\/m3-performance-mattress-new","button2_text":"Shop Mattresses","button2_link":"shopify:\/\/collections\/mattresses","image_on_left":false}},"feature_block_zGKadV":{"type":"feature_block","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/628d91e719a0547fac160d553a645bda07cd5311.png","label":"VER-TEX PERFORMANCE® SHEETS","title":"Covered In Cool","description":"<p>Inspired by your favorite activewear, our instant-cooling Ver-Tex Performance® Sheets pull heat and moisture away from your body on contact—so your nights start cool and stay that way. Built for breathability and finished with a silky-smooth touch, they’re designed for next-level comfort and uninterrupted sleep that helps your body recharge overnight.<\/p>","button1_text":"Shop Ver-Tex Sheet Set","button1_link":"shopify:\/\/products\/ver-tex-sheet-set","button2_text":"Shop Sheets","button2_link":"shopify:\/\/collections\/sheets","image_on_left":true}},"feature_block_8kVy9F":{"type":"feature_block","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/comforter-BG-PP-Sheets-FeatureBlock-1200x700_jj5ztc.png","label":"PERFORMANCE® COMFORTER","title":"Sleep Smarter, Not Hotter.","description":"<p>The ultra-soft Performance® Comforter features our Climacore® Intelligent Insulation—a high-tech, breathable fill that keeps air flowing and warmth balanced, without ever weighing you down. Choose Light, Medium, or Ultra Weight to match your sleep style and the season.<\/p>","button1_text":"Shop Comforter","button1_link":"shopify:\/\/products\/performance-comforter","button2_text":"Shop Bedding","button2_link":"shopify:\/\/collections\/bedgear-home","image_on_left":false}}},"block_order":["feature_block_jRVJKh","feature_block_Ezik3T","feature_block_zGKadV","feature_block_8kVy9F"],"settings":{"heading_text":"RECOVER TONIGHT","heading_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Rebound_Tomorrow.png","subheading":"Check out P.J.'s picks and personalize your own Performance® Sleep System today."}},"testimonials_mUabmx":{"type":"testimonials","blocks":{"testimonials_list_8eCRMr":{"type":"testimonials_list","settings":{"review_rating":"5","title":"LOVE THIS PILLOW!!!!!","text":"Tried this pillow in the store. Cannot WAIT to go to bed tonight! Seriously was the best pillow I've laid my head on. I think I've spent over $1,000 to find the right pillow. I can already tell, this is it!!!","author_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/user-circle-02_e5d8ca8e-9b7d-4d50-ac09-93f7d5409e7a.svg","author":"JENNIFER","verified_text":"Verified Buyer","verified_icon":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/verified.png","featured_product":"night-ice-performance-pillow","featured_product_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/01-NIGHT_ICE-1.0-ProductShot-Main_0432e2a4-3a2f-40bb-b3f0-48674c79b69d.jpg","button_label":"Shop Now"}},"testimonials_list_zNedby":{"type":"testimonials_list","settings":{"review_rating":"5","title":"SO COOL🤩","text":"These sheets are so soft and cool to the touch. This is the first time I've felt like I haven't overheated in my bed. Worth every penny!!!","author_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/user-circle-02_e5d8ca8e-9b7d-4d50-ac09-93f7d5409e7a.svg","author":"BENJAMIN","verified_text":"Verified Buyer","verified_icon":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/verified.png","featured_produc